<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>普通人用AI on 知行社</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/tags/%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%A8ai/</link><description>Recent content in 普通人用AI on 知行社</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/tags/%E6%99%AE%E9%80%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%94%A8ai/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>OpenClaw团队有岗位没手艺？用了2个月的升级方案</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/openclaw%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%B2%97%E4%BD%8D%E6%B2%A1%E6%89%8B%E8%89%BA%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%862%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</link><pubDate>Sat, 14 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/openclaw%E5%9B%A2%E9%98%9F%E6%9C%89%E5%B2%97%E4%BD%8D%E6%B2%A1%E6%89%8B%E8%89%BA%E7%94%A8%E4%BA%862%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E7%9A%84%E5%8D%87%E7%BA%A7%E6%96%B9%E6%A1%88/</guid><description>一个FMCG渠道销售，用2个月时间搭了一支AI团队：情报官、写手、分析师、设计师。不是程序员，靠的是配置文件和踩坑经验。这篇是升级方案——发现了集体缺的那样东西。</description></item><item><title>我让 AI「审判」了上个月的账单，结果被骂哭了</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E6%88%91%E8%AE%A9ai%E5%AE%A1%E5%88%A4%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A6%E5%8D%95/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E6%88%91%E8%AE%A9ai%E5%AE%A1%E5%88%A4%E4%BA%86%E4%B8%8A%E4%B8%AA%E6%9C%88%E7%9A%84%E8%B4%A6%E5%8D%95/</guid><description>一个FMCG从业者用AI审判自己的月度账单。不是程序员，没有代码，照样让AI替自己做了一件记账App永远做不到的事——真正扎心。</description></item><item><title>结构化输出：省掉70%的人工整理时间（以及它不适合的场景）</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8C%96%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E7%9C%8170%E5%90%8E%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/</link><pubDate>Tue, 10 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%84%E5%8C%96%E8%BE%93%E5%87%BA%E7%9C%8170%E5%90%8E%E5%A4%84%E7%90%86%E6%97%B6%E9%97%B4/</guid><description>不是程序员，也能让AI输出结构化数据，省掉70%手工整理时间。一个做快消品渠道销售的人，怎么把开发者才会用的技巧变成日常工作流——含具体示例。</description></item><item><title>别解释了，点亮「他」</title><link>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E5%88%AB%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A%E4%BA%86%E7%82%B9%E4%BA%AE%E4%BB%96/</link><pubDate>Thu, 05 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://blog.zhixingshe.cc/posts/%E5%88%AB%E8%A7%A3%E9%87%8A%E4%BA%86%E7%82%B9%E4%BA%AE%E4%BB%96/</guid><description>跟身边人聊AI总没反应？不是他们不聪明，是你讲错了。一个FMCG从业者怎么让周围人真正相信AI能改变工作——不靠解释，靠让他们看见。</description></item></channel></rss>